Text:
Malestrom, I need your help again!
For the design of home wind turbine I need some info about guyed lattice towers. I hope the following books can help and i will be very thankful to you if you succeed to find them. Thanks!
1.Comprehensive Design of Steel Structures - By Punmia, Ashok Kumar Jain, B.C. Punmia
 Communication structures - By Brian Ward Smith
2.Dynamic response of lattice towers and guyed masts - By Madugula K. S. Murty, Structural Engineering Institute.
3.Lattice tower and mast - British Standards Institution - Part 1-4
